title: The.Incredible.Adventures.of.Van.Helsing.Update.v1.2.2.Incl.7.DL
description:

Included DLCs:

- Scenario DLC
- Treasure Hunter Perk
- Veteran Mutliplayer Skin
- Blue Blood
- Thaumaturge
- Arcane Mechanic

1. Install The Incredible Adventures of Van Helsing  
2. Install Update from the /Update folder to your

3. Copy over the cracked content from the /Crack dir
